  "text": "The present contribution provides a basis for the study of superfield Lagrangian description of the more general D = 4 interacting system including supermembrane, supergravity and matter multiplets (see [CITATION_1] for the spacetime component study), in particular of the D = 4 representative of the family of \"curious supergravity theory\" described in [CITATION_2] .",
